Description of folders:
constants - AS constants folder
controller - AS controller folder
deploy - folder that need to be place on the web server public html folder
fla - source flash files
ftp - configuration files to connect to the Webhostingpad web server
graphics - any graphics files to create or prototype application
lib - folder that needs to be placed one level up the public html folder on the web server.  Contains password for database
model - AS model folder
view - AS view folder

== DEPLOY WARNINGS
+ If you ever change the MySQL user or password on WebHostingPad.com you need to add the user to the database that you want to grant them access to.  Do this by:
1) Creating the user
2) Press the 'Add user' and select the appropriate privileges.